wageTypes.name: Monatslohn
wageTypes.valueExpression: var values = GetCaseValues("Monatslohn", "Beschäftigungsgrad"); return values["Monatslohn"] * values["Beschäftigungsgrad"];

wageTypes.name: Stundenlohn
wageTypes.valueExpression: var values = GetCaseValues("Anzahl Stunden", "Stundenlohn"); return values["Anzahl Stunden"] * values["Stundenlohn"];

wageTypes.name: Lohndeckung
wageTypes.valueExpression: var results = GetPeriodWageTypeResults(new(101, 1, PayrunJobStatus.Legal)).Values(); return results.Any() ? (results[0] < 3000 ? 3000-results[0] : 0) : 0

wageTypes.name: Quellensteuer
wageTypes.valueExpression: var lookup = GetLookup<decimal>("Quellensteuer", new Key("B", 2, CaseValue["Location"].Value, CaseValue["Geburtsdatum"].ValueAs<DateTime>().Age(PeriodStart) >= 50 ? 50 : 0, (decimal)CaseValue["Stundenlohn"] > 70m ? "Y" : "N" )); return lookup != null ? Collector["QST Basis"] * lookup : 0;

wageTypes.name: Sonderbonus
wageTypes.valueExpression: var lookup = GetRangeLookup<decimal>("Sonderbonus", WageType[101]); return lookup != null ? WageType[101] * lookup : 0;

wageTypes.name: SharedWage
wageTypes.valueExpression: var lookup = GetLookup<decimal>("PartnerCountries", "CH"); return lookup != null ? lookup * WageType[101] : WageType[101];

wageTypes.name: Case Value Attributes
wageTypes.valueExpression1: var caseValue = GetRawCaseValue("Monatslohn", PeriodEnd); if (caseValue == null || caseValue.Attributes == null || !caseValue.Attributes.ContainsKey("MyValueAttribute")) return 0; return caseValue.Attributes["MyValueAttribute"];
wageTypes.valueExpression: var caseValue = GetRawCaseValue("Monatslohn", PeriodEnd); return caseValue == null ? 0 : caseValue.Attributes == null ? -1 : caseValue.Attributes.GetValue<decimal>("MyValueAttribute");
